  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "1. Shelter: Temporary shelter construction support\r\n\r\n2. Food & Nutrition: Food and nutrition provided to needy children and women\r\n\r\n3. Education and Child protection: Educational materials (Uniform, books) and Child friendly activities and disaster preparedness activities will be performed. School construction and renovation will be supported.\r\n\r\n4. WASH: Water supply tank construction through material support. Hygiene kit will also be provided.\r\n\r\n5. Livelihood restoration: Agricultural inputs (like seed) support will be provided. Animal husbandry and small enterprises will be supported.\r\n\r\n6. Health facilities: Health post/centres will be repaired/maintained. Health camps will be conducted."
    },
    "ne": null
